# make data array from files

doy_start = -25
doy_end = -18

# Loop through each NDVI image
mcaz_ndvi_das = []
for ndvi_path in mcaz_ndvi_paths:
    ndvi_path = Path(ndvi_path)

    # Get date from file name
    doy = ndvi_path.name[doy_start:doy_end]
    date = pd.to_datetime(doy, format='%Y%j')

    # Open dataset
    da = rxr.open_rasterio(ndvi_path, mask_and_scale=True).squeeze()

    # Add date dimension and clean up metadata
    da = da.assign_coords({'date': date})
    da = da.expand_dims({'date': 1})
    da.name = 'NDVI'

    # Prepare for concatenation
    mcaz_ndvi_das.append(da)

# Select data by date ranges
ndvi_1017 = da.sel(date=slice('2010-01-01', '2017-12-31'))
ndvi_1825 = da.sel(date=slice('2018-01-01', '2025-12-31'))
# Take temporal mean by date dimension
ndvi_1017_mean = ndvi_1017.mean(dim='date')
ndvi_1825_mean = ndvi_1825.mean(dim='date')
# Compute NDVI change through subtraction
ndvi_change = ndvi_1825_mean - ndvi_1017_mean

ndvi_change
